  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening socio-economic development in Chile: Using UK expertise to promote low-carbon districts and shared street use in Chile</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To use UK experience to create a change in street use in Santiago by implementing a low carbon district with green transport infrastructure and data collection tools to raise civil society awareness of climate change and change people&apos;s attitudes towards sustainable transport infrastructure. Promoting the development of &quot;Smarter&quot; cities in Chile has the potential to generate further UK-Chile commercial and policy collaboration in the future.</narrative>
  </description>
